.TH TRANSCRIBE-DAEMON 1 "February 2025" "dictee 0.99" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
transcribe-daemon \- speech recognition daemon with preloaded model
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B transcribe-daemon
.RI [ model_dir ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B transcribe-daemon
starts a daemon that keeps the Parakeet TDT model loaded in memory,
allowing fast repeated transcriptions via
.BR transcribe-client (1).
.PP
The daemon listens on a Unix socket at /tmp/transcribe.sock
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.I model_dir
Path to TDT model directory (default: /usr/share/dictee/tdt)
.SH SYSTEMD
To run as a user service:
.PP
.RS
systemctl --user enable --now dictee
.RE
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR transcribe-client (1),
.BR transcribe (1),
.BR dictee (1)
.SH AUTHOR
rcspam <rcspams@gmail.com>
